Weh di werd Bileez kohn frahn noh soh klyaa, bot di fos rekad dehn deh eena di jernal a di Domineekan prees Fray Jose Delgado, bak eena 1677. Delgado rikaad di nayhn a chree big-taim riva weh hihn mi kraas wen ih mi-di chravl lang di Kyaribeeyan Koas: Rio Soyte, Rio Xibun, ahn Rio Balis.
Wen wi seh sivilizayshan wi di taak bowt wahn big taim soashal sistim weh ga dehnya ting: siti laif, wahn way fi rait noh jos taak, ahn wahn way how kolcha ahn naycha difrant, wid hai-standin kolcha peepl di tek chaaj a tingz.
Wen yu tink bowt Bileez, yu tink bowt it laik Sentral Amerikan plos Kyaribeeyan, ahn ih ga schrang kanekshan wid di too reejan dehn. Bileez da wahn memba a di Kyaribeeyan Kamyooniti (CARICOM), di Kamyooniti a Latin Amerikan ahn Kyaribeeyan Staytz (CELAC), ahn di Sentral Amerikan Intigrayshan Sistim (SICA).
